            . I am a constable. The prisoner went with the prosecutrix and me to the pawnbrokers, and the things were delivered to me.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence.</p>
               <p>Mistress used to keep me short of victuals, so I pawned these things to get me necessaries.</p>
               <p>Prosecutrix. She was with me but a fortnight. She could not need all that money for victuals; but I have neighbours here that know there is no want of that sort at my house.</p>
